  "text": "ABCB1 3435C>T was in linkage equilibrium with both CYP3A4*1B and CYP3A5*3C (DV = 0.183 and 0.0933, respectively). Linkage disequilibrium was apparent between CYP3A4*1B and CYP3A5*3C (DV = 0.656), as described previously [CITATION_1] .",
